-- Anglo CEO Carroll Says “Bullish” Across Commodity Spread
-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 2011-02-08T09:35:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-08/anglo-american-ceo-carroll-says-he-is-bullish-across-commodity-spread.html
  Anglo American Plc ’s Chief Executive
Officer Cynthia Carroll said she is “pretty bullish across the
commodity spread.”  Carroll is “high” on copper and metallurgical coal,
“very bullish” on platinum and “continues to believe” in
iron ore,’’ she said in an interview in  Cape Town  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
